00:22:55.160 --> 00:22:59.870 align:middle line:84%
And same with you and
same with everybody else.

00:22:59.870 --> 00:23:03.010 align:middle line:84%
Then a lifetime is
a very short time.

00:23:03.010 --> 00:23:03.960 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It is.

00:23:03.960 --> 00:23:05.620 align:middle line:84%
>>RUIZ: Let's say if
we live 100 years.

00:23:05.620 --> 00:23:07.460 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes, it's so short.

00:23:07.460 --> 00:23:09.790 align:middle line:90%
>>RUIZ: 100 years with eternity.

00:23:09.790 --> 00:23:11.920 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: In the soul's
journey, it is so short.

00:23:11.920 --> 00:23:13.782 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:23:13.782 --> 00:23:15.240 align:middle line:84%
>>RUIZ: Then the
question is, well,

00:23:15.240 --> 00:23:16.900 align:middle line:84%
what are we going
to do in the time

00:23:16.900 --> 00:23:18.460 align:middle line:84%
that we live in our
physical bodies?

00:23:18.460 --> 00:23:19.340 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:23:19.340 --> 00:23:20.140 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:23:20.140 --> 00:23:22.120 align:middle line:84%
>>RUIZ: If we are
impeccable with the word,

00:23:22.120 --> 00:23:27.670 align:middle line:84%
we really can enjoy our
life in every single moment.

00:23:27.670 --> 00:23:28.990 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That is such a key.

00:23:28.990 --> 00:23:30.680 align:middle line:90%
That is absolutely the key.

00:23:30.680 --> 00:23:31.480 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:23:31.480 --> 00:23:36.730 align:middle line:84%
With the however many
days we have in this body,

00:23:36.730 --> 00:23:39.610 align:middle line:84%
what are we going to
do with those days?

00:23:39.610 --> 00:23:41.680 align:middle line:84%
And being impeccable
with your word,

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:46.390 align:middle line:84%
not taking things personally,
to waste that energy, to really

00:23:46.390 --> 00:23:50.622 align:middle line:84%
be fully authentic, and to get
things done, to move forward.

00:23:50.622 --> 00:23:51.580 align:middle line:90%
Don't make assumptions.

00:23:51.580 --> 00:23:53.470 align:middle line:84%
Don't waste your energy
on that, but really

00:23:53.470 --> 00:23:55.510 align:middle line:90%
to always do your best.

00:23:55.510 --> 00:24:01.323 align:middle line:84%
>>RUIZ: And be skeptical,
but learn to listen.

00:24:01.323 --> 00:24:02.990 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's a big
one, the fifth one.

00:24:02.990 --> 00:24:04.030 align:middle line:84%
>>RUIZ: It's the
fifth agreement.

00:24:04.030 --> 00:24:06.040 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Before we go there, I
want you to take a look here

00:24:06.040 --> 00:24:08.290 align:middle line:84%
at Don Miguel talking
about the four agreements.

00:24:08.290 --> 00:24:09.599 align:middle line:90%
Take a look at this.

00:24:09.599 --> 00:24:12.094 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:24:12.094 --> 00:24:24.070 align:middle line:90%


00:24:24.070 --> 00:24:27.280 align:middle line:84%
>> What you are seeing and
hearing right now is nothing

00:24:27.280 --> 00:24:29.380 align:middle line:90%
but a dream.

00:24:29.380 --> 00:24:32.990 align:middle line:84%
You're dreaming right
now in this moment.

00:24:32.990 --> 00:24:35.660 align:middle line:84%
