domestication of humans.

00:25:32.860 --> 00:25:35.680 align:middle line:84%
We trust what we
believe, and our beliefs

00:25:35.680 --> 00:25:37.535 align:middle line:90%
set us up for suffering.

00:25:37.535 --> 00:25:40.450 align:middle line:90%


00:25:40.450 --> 00:25:43.460 align:middle line:84%
In the dream of the planet,
it is normal for humans

00:25:43.460 --> 00:25:49.660 align:middle line:84%
to suffer, to live in fear,
and to create emotional dramas.

00:25:49.660 --> 00:25:53.110 align:middle line:84%
Our personal dream can also
become an ongoing nightmare,

00:25:53.110 --> 00:25:57.170 align:middle line:84%
where we suffer and
live in a state of fear.

00:25:57.170 --> 00:26:00.540 align:middle line:84%
But we don't need to
dream a nightmare.

00:26:00.540 --> 00:26:05.170 align:middle line:84%
It is possible to
enjoy a pleasant dream.

00:26:05.170 --> 00:26:06.790 align:middle line:10%
There are thousands
of agreements

00:26:06.790 --> 00:26:10.850 align:middle line:10%
you have made with
yourself, with other people,

00:26:10.850 --> 00:26:16.310 align:middle line:10%
with God, with society, with
your parents, with your spouse,

00:26:16.310 --> 00:26:18.910 align:middle line:10%
with your children.

00:26:18.910 --> 00:26:21.070 align:middle line:84%
But the most
important agreements

00:26:21.070 --> 00:26:23.940 align:middle line:84%
are the ones you
made with yourself.

00:26:23.940 --> 00:26:27.950 align:middle line:84%
In these agreements, you
tell yourself who you are,

00:26:27.950 --> 00:26:33.600 align:middle line:84%
what you feel, what you
believe, and how to behave.

00:26:33.600 --> 00:26:36.580 align:middle line:84%
One single agreement
is not such a problem,

00:26:36.580 --> 00:26:39.780 align:middle line:84%
but we have many agreements
that make us suffer,

00:26:39.780 --> 00:26:41.190 align:middle line:90%
that make us fail in life.

00:26:41.190 --> 00:26:44.970 align:middle line:90%


00:26:44.970 --> 00:26:48.510 align:middle line:84%
If you want to live a life
of joy and fulfillment,

00:26:48.510 --> 00:26:51.450 align:middle line:84%
you have to find the courage
to break those agreements that

00:26:51.450 --> 00:26:54.510 align:middle line:84%
are fear-based and claim
your personal power.

00:26:54.510 --> 00:26:57.090 align:middle line:90%


00:26:57.090 --> 00:27:00.090 align:middle line:10%
When we're finally ready
to change our agreements,

00:27:00.090 --> 00:27:02.970 align:middle line:10%
there are four very
powerful agreements

00:27:02.970 --> 00:27:06.420 align:middle line:10%
that will help us break those
agreements that come from fear

00:27:06.420 --> 00:27:09.340 align:middle line:10%
and deplete our energy.

00:27:09.340 --> 00:27:11.830 align:middle line:10%
You need a very
strong will in order

00:27:11.830 --> 00:27:14.610 align:middle line:10%
to adopt the four agreements.

00:27:14.610 --> 00:27:16.530 align:middle line:84%
But if you can begin
to live your life

00:27:16.530 --> 00:27:20.440 align:middle line:84%
with these agreements, the
transformation in your life

00:27:20.440 --> 00:27:21.240 align:middle line:90%
will be amazing.

00:27:21.240 --> 00:27:23.670 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:27:23.670 --> 00:27:30.000 align:middle line:90%


00:27:30.000 --> 00:27:32.850 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's true, you do
need a very strong will--

00:27:32.850 --> 00:27:33.900 align:middle line:90%
>>RUIZ: Definitely.

00:27:33.900 --> 00:27:36.480 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --To live by
these four agreements.

00:27:36.480 --> 00:27:39.000 align:middle line:84%
And you were
mentioning the fifth.

00:27:39.000 --> 00:27:40.750 align:middle line:84%
Tell me about the
fifth agreement.

00:27:40.750 --> 00:27:44.850 align:middle line:84%
>>RUIZ: It's be skeptical,
but learn to listen.

00:27:44.850 --> 00:27:46.290 align:middle line:10%
Think when we
practice these four

00:27:46.290 --> 00:27:53.610 align:middle line:10%
agreements for a certain time,
you can say for a long time,

00:27:53.610 --> 00:27:58.010 align:middle line:10%
the moment comes I shall really
live in these four agreements.

00:27:58.010 --> 00:28:02.060 align:middle line:10%
Shall not pretend that you are
living the four agreements.

00:28:02.060 --> 00:28:08.460 align:middle line:84%
And that's when the
fifth agreement start.

00:28:08.460 --> 00:28:13.560 align:middle line:84%
Be skeptical, but
learn to listen.

00:28:13.560 --> 00:28:16.710 align:middle line:84%
